                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210912-124-off721 t18210912-124-cd722"></join>, one shirt, value 3 s.; four handkerchiefs, value 7 s., and one pair of stockings, value 1 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18210912-124-victim1353" type="victimName">
